Rules of state

1. Only usable with class componenets   (Technicall, can use with 'hooks' system. To discuss later)
2. You will confuse props with state :(
3. 'State' is a JS object that contains data relevant to the componenets
4. Updating 'State' almost instantly causees a re-render
5. State must be initialized wihen a component is created
6. State can ONLY be updated using the function 'setState'